title: クレーンゲーム大成功！

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: I can't believe we got so many...! Every 'Paka Puchi' is so cute~.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: But still, Trainer's crane skills are extraordinary, truly pro-level!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Maybe if I ask Trainer, they could easily grab that spider plushie too...
Yeah, let's go try it right away!
